snippet.title: Treehouse, The gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Treehouse, The, Dos PC game produced by Broderbund in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/treehouse-the/6435/
Playing through a few mini-games in this kids educational adventure game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
